description:
Kei is a young female revolutionary whom http://anidb.net/ch7558 [Kaneda] meets and becomes enamoured with on his quest to find http://anidb.net/ch7560 [Tetsuo]. She is a member of an anti-government faction that Ryu and Nezu are also involved in. Although she does not possess preternatural abilities, Kei is employed by the espers as a type of medium on several occasions.
Source: wikipedia.org
name: Kei
